{"tid":383501,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"22:25【蜘蛛俠：英雄歸來 Spider-Man: Homecoming 2017】","createTime":"2017-09-01T13:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T15:31:13.000Z","uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0428ed0b6e0a2fa7ee35b6a6c840c7fbc52c5a31","tid":383501,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.simbla.com%2F871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a%2Fiusee&d=jNqal1Y62jF460GvPJUSjwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=fcd15487\" target=\"_blank\">http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee</a><br />\n<br />\n　　影片講述了蜘蛛俠在鋼鐵俠&ldquo;導師&rdquo;的幫助下對抗終極反派禿鷹的故事。經歷了美隊3中的復聯內戰後，彼得&middot;帕克（湯姆&middot;赫蘭德 飾）回到普通高中生活，並受到鋼鐵俠托尼&middot;斯塔克（小羅伯特&middot;唐尼 飾）的指導與暗中關注。一心想要證明自己能力的小蜘蛛，在一場銀行劫案後遭遇了擁有外星終極武器的反派禿鷹（邁克爾&middot;基頓 飾），卻因一時心急而使萬千生命陷入危機。此時，鋼鐵俠卻意外收回了贈予蜘蛛俠的無敵戰衣，這對於遭遇重創的蜘蛛俠無異於雪上加霜。他能否證明自己的能力，成功保衛家園成為懸念，而他&ldquo;獲得復聯入場券&rdquo;的夢想，也看似遙遙無期&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://edwardmovieclub.com/wp-content/uploads/094218.90429223_1000X1000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedwardmovieclub.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F094218.90429223_1000X1000.jpg&h=22ec9b7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b513f542f8fb326ec4d4c36a8fd548dc14fcf4c","tid":383501,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"09d576e6d080a1c5247b1d0fa785ed29bac2a59c","tid":383501,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:04:32.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"347430cac9ce5b5b29ff19abf61defbb9b8a4bde","tid":383501,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"[img][/img]"},{"pid":"535ef05d6eb37389b7c413f787a0e0adf8d28849","tid":383501,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy